<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL14">
<l>vaṇṭiṉa muraluñ cōlai mayiliṉa māluñ cōlai</l>
<l>koṇṭalmī taṇavuñ cōlai kuyiliṉaṅ kūvuñ cōlai</l>
<l>aṇṭarkō ṉamaruñ cōlai yaṇitiru varaṅka meṉṉā</l>
<l>miṇṭarpāyn tuṇṇuñ cōṟṟai vilakkināyk kiṭumi ṉīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘Śrīraṅgam is adorned with groves where swarms of bees hum;</l>
<l rend="indent">where musters of peacocks dance;</l>
<l rend="indent">which the clouds approach;</l>
<l rend="indent">where flocks of koels coo;</l>
<l rend="indent">where the Lord of the Celestials dwells!’</l>
<l>Removing the food eagerly eaten by the ignorant people who do not say [thus]</l>
<l>you give it to the dogs!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
